name: Teleport
description:
Quickly move or duplicate your selection to a new page via the Quick Action Search Bar (âŒ˜+/)

-


Teleport option creates a new page and moves the current selection to that page.


Duplicate and Teleport option creates a new page and sends a duplicate of the current selection to that page.


Optionally name the new page in the quick action parameters, otherwise the new page will be called "Teleported Here" by default.
